[{"id":"01","title":"INTRODUCTION","lines":["1. INTRODUCTION","1.1 The Need for a Civilization Layer","The simulation age collapses the boundaries between:","humans and AI","physical and digital","identity and simulation","presence and representation","Traditional identity systems fail because they assume:","faces are real","voices are real","accounts are real","institutions can verify truth","These assumptions no longer hold.","Identity must evolve into:","a sovereign, embodied, cryptographic, crossplatform primitive.","This primitive becomes the foundation of a new civilization layer.","1.2 The MyShape Civilization Thesis","The MyShape Civilization Layer is built on three principles:","1. Identity is the substrate of civilization","Without identity, no society can coordinate.","2. Geometry is the substrate of identity","Only the individual can generate uncopyable structure.","3. Zeroknowledge is the substrate of trust","Truth must be provable without exposure.","These principles define the longterm evolution of MyShape.","1.3 The FourEpoch Roadmap","The MyShape roadmap spans 20+ years and unfolds in four epochs:","Epoch I — Genesis (2025–2027)","Identity = Geometry","motion integrity","geometric identity","ZK presence","MVP ecosystem","early developer integrations","This epoch establishes the primitive.","Epoch II — Protocolization (2027–2030)","Identity = Protocol","crossplatform verification","multiagent identity","tokenomics activation","developer ecosystem","governance v1","This epoch establishes the infrastructure.","Epoch III — Ecosystem Expansion (2030–2035)","Identity = Substrate","XR identity","AI identity","robotics identity","multiworld presence","crosschain identity","This epoch establishes the ecosystem.","Epoch IV — Civilization Layer (2035–2045+)","Identity = Civilization","identitybound governance","identitybound economies","identitybound social systems","multispecies coordination","global identity substrate","This epoch establishes the civilization."]},{"id":"02","title":"THE CIVILIZATION LAYER PRINCIPLES","lines":["2. THE CIVILIZATION LAYER PRINCIPLES","The Civilization Layer is built on five foundational principles.","2.1 Embodied Sovereignty","Identity must be:","generated by the individual","owned by the individual","independent of platforms","independent of institutions","Sovereignty begins with embodiment.","2.2 MultiSpecies Coexistence","The future includes:","humans","AI agents","hybrid agents","autonomous systems","robots","virtual entities","Identity must be speciesagnostic.","2.3 ZeroKnowledge Society","A civilization where:","truth is provable","privacy is preserved","identity is sovereign","verification is universal","This is the ZK civilization.","2.4 CrossWorld Continuity","Identity must persist across:","physical world","virtual worlds","AI worlds","simulation layers","multiagent environments","Identity becomes the connective tissue of reality.","2.5 CivilizationScale Coordination","The Civilization Layer enables:","identitybound governance","identitybound economies","identitybound social systems","identitybound AI alignment","Identity becomes the coordination substrate of the future.","3. EPOCH I — GENESIS ROADMAP (2025–2027)","Identity = Geometry","Epoch I establishes the primitive: the idea that identity is not visual, not narrative, not institutional — but geometric.","This epoch focuses on building the irreducible core.","3.1 Technical Milestones","1. Motion Integrity Engine (MIE) v1","kinematic tensor extraction","curvature signatures","noisebased detection","antireplay primitives","2. Geometry Engine (GE) v1","invariant extraction","manifold projection","canonicalization","3. ZKMG &amp; ZKMIP v1","first zeroknowledge motion proofs","&lt;1 KB proof size","&lt;10 ms verification","4. OnDevice Runtime v1","iOS / Android","WebAssembly","Unity/Unreal","5. Genesis Identity Standard","presence","liveness","uniqueness","3.2 Ecosystem Milestones","first developer SDK","first social integrations","first XR integrations","first AI agent integrations","first robotics experiments","3.3 Economic Milestones","$PULSE minting v1","$ENERGY pricing v1","$SHAPE treasury initialization","3.4 Governance Milestones","identityweighted governance v0","presenceverified voting","protocol constitution draft","3.5 Civilization Outcomes","Epoch I establishes:","the primitive","the math","the cryptography","the presence standard","the first real human identity layer","This is the birth of geometric identity.","4. EPOCH II — PROTOCOLIZATION ROADMAP (2027–2030)","Identity = Protocol","Epoch II transforms MyShape from a product into a protocol.","This epoch focuses on infrastructure, standardization, and crossplatform adoption.","4.1 Technical Milestones","1. Motion Integrity Engine v2","multisensor fusion","IMU–vision correlation","antisynthesis v2","2. Geometry Engine v2","manifold stability","crossdevice consistency","hybrid identity support","3. ZKMG &amp; ZKMIP v2","&lt;512 bytes proofs","&lt;1 ms verification","onchain compatibility","4. Universal Verification Standard (UVS)","crossplatform identity handshake","agent declaration protocol","presence signature format","4.2 Ecosystem Milestones","major social platform integrations","major XR world integrations","major AI agent frameworks","robotics SDK v1","crosschain identity bridges","4.3 Economic Milestones","$PULSE issuance curve v2","$ENERGY burn economics v2","$SHAPE governance activation","4.4 Governance Milestones","ZK governance v1","identityweighted quadratic voting","multisig upgrade council","4.5 Civilization Outcomes","Epoch II establishes:","the protocol","the standards","the verification layer","the multiagent identity model","Identity becomes infrastructure.","5. EPOCH III — ECOSYSTEM EXPANSION ROADMAP (2030–2035)","Identity = Substrate","Epoch III transforms MyShape into a global identity substrate spanning physical, digital, and AI environments.","5.1 Technical Milestones","1. Motion Integrity Engine v3","biomechanical modeling","neuromuscular noise simulation","antiAI v3 (diffusion/transformerresistant)","2. Geometry Engine v3","multiworld geometry","XRnative geometry","roboticsnative geometry","3. ZKMG &amp; ZKMIP v3","sub256 byte proofs","hardware acceleration","universal verifier","5.2 Ecosystem Milestones","XR identity standard","AI identity standard","robotics identity standard","crossworld identity portability","multiagent coordination networks","5.3 Economic Milestones","identitybound assets","presencebased economies","multiagent economic systems","$SHAPEbased ecosystem treasury","5.4 Governance Milestones","identitybound governance","presenceweighted global voting","multiagent governance frameworks","5.5 Civilization Outcomes","Epoch III establishes:","identity across worlds","identity across species","identity across platforms","identity across agents","Identity becomes the substrate of digital civilization.","6. EPOCH IV — CIVILIZATION LAYER ROADMAP (2035–2045+)","Identity = Civilization","Epoch IV is the longterm vision: MyShape becomes the identity substrate of a multispecies, multiworld civilization.","6.1 Technical Milestones","universal identity kernel","crossspecies identity protocols","embodied AI identity","multiworld presence engine","civilizationscale ZK systems","6.2 Ecosystem Milestones","global identity infrastructure","crossworld governance","identitybound social systems","identitybound economies","identitybound AI alignment","6.3 Economic Milestones","civilizationscale $ENERGY markets","identitybound economic primitives","multiagent economic coordination","6.4 Governance Milestones","identityverified global governance","multiagent constitutional systems","presenceweighted democratic structures","6.5 Civilization Outcomes","Epoch IV establishes:","a ZK civilization","a multispecies identity substrate","a crossworld coordination layer","a sovereign identity foundation for humanity and AI","Identity becomes the operating system of civilization."]},{"id":"07","title":"CONCLUSION","lines":["7. CONCLUSION","The MyShape Roadmap &amp; Civilization Layer defines a multidecade evolution:","From geometry → to protocol → to ecosystem → to civilization.","MyShape is not a company. Not a product. Not an app.","It is:","a new identity primitive","a new economic substrate","a new governance foundation","a new multispecies coordination layer","a new civilizational infrastructure","This is the identity layer of the next internet and the coordination layer of the next civilization."]}]